    "His 1907 thesis on art and empathy was draws from the 19th-century aesthetic ideas of Novalis and Schlegel.": [
        [
            98,
            106,
            [
                "Schlemiel",
                "Schiebel"
            ]
        ]
    ],
    "But Worringer's method owes a great deal to the esthetic theories of Theodor Lipps (1854-1914) and the art history of <a href=\"/riegla\">Alo\u00efs Riegl</a>.": [
        [
            4,
