    "However, it is here that the problems with such a global theory based on style begin to appear.": [],
    "Gothic art becomes defined as any style not shaped by classically inspired culture.": [],
    "Worringer's dichotomies become sharper and more forced than in his earlier work: North vs South, abstraction vs empathy, renaissance vs gothic.": [
        [
